fields.name: Tesla Model X Long Range 2021
fields.description: Everyone’s favorite SUV with bird-inspired doors is making a comeback for the 2022 model year. With 360 miles of range, an optional 7-seat interior, and more quirks than Elon Musk himself, the 2022 Model X won’t fail to impress. The only downside of the new Model X is its pricey starting point which just crests the $100,000 mark, including destination.
fields.list: Range: 360 miles / Drivetrain: AWD / Acceleration: 0-60 in 3.8 seconds
